      <title>沙特阿拉伯国王萨勒曼肺部炎症痊愈</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-09/saudi-arabia-s-king-salman-recovers-from-lung-inflammation</link>
      <description><![CDATA[沙特阿拉伯国王萨勒曼·本·阿卜杜勒阿齐兹已从肺部炎症中康复，该消息于周日由沙特阿拉伯国家通讯社首次报道。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-09/saudi-arabia-s-king-salman-recovers-from-lung-inflammation</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 09 Oct 2024 13:59:28 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>喀麦隆债券因投资者权衡政治稳定风险而下跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-09/cameroon-bonds-drop-as-investors-weigh-political-stability-risk</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于对该国总统健康状况的猜测引发了人们对潜在继任之争的担忧，喀麦隆美元债券连续第三天下跌。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-09/cameroon-bonds-drop-as-investors-weigh-political-stability-risk</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 09 Oct 2024 13:51:23 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>KKR 与美国司法部就交易审查发生争执，这对私募股权公司来说是个不祥之兆</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-09/kkr-spars-with-doj-over-deal-reviews-in-bad-omen-for-pe-firms</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着美国当局加强对私募股权行业的审查，KKR&amp;Co. 和司法部正在就要求该公司高管对收购相关披露承担更多责任一事展开争论。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-09/kkr-spars-with-doj-over-deal-reviews-in-bad-omen-for-pe-firms</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 09 Oct 2024 13:15:47 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>斯塔默表示不排除提高企业工资税的可能性</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-09/starmer-leaves-open-prospect-of-raising-uk-business-payroll-tax</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国政府正在想方设法填补其所继承的 220 亿英镑（288 亿美元）公共财政漏洞，基尔·斯塔默 (Keir Starmer) 在即将出台的英国预算中保留了提高企业工资税的可能性。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-09/starmer-leaves-open-prospect-of-raising-uk-business-payroll-tax</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 09 Oct 2024 13:15:19 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>多重冲突推高通胀，以色列维持利率不变</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-09/israel-holds-rates-as-multi-front-conflict-pushes-up-inflation</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于加沙和黎巴嫩的冲突造成通胀压力，并阻止该国加入全球宽松周期，以色列央行在下调经济增长预测的同时仍维持利率不变。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-09/israel-holds-rates-as-multi-front-conflict-pushes-up-inflation</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 09 Oct 2024 13:01:22 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>华尔街海湾繁荣面临伊朗-以色列紧张局势的风险</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-09/mideast-latest-wall-street-s-gulf-boom-faces-risks-from-iran-israel-tensions</link>
      <description><![CDATA[华尔街巨头纷纷涌入中东，希望从该地区巨大的石油财富中分一杯羹，但伊朗和以色列之间不断升级的紧张局势却带来了新的不确定性。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-09/mideast-latest-wall-street-s-gulf-boom-faces-risks-from-iran-israel-tensions</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 09 Oct 2024 12:43:48 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>南非推出签证改革措施，旨在吸引技术人才</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-09/south-africa-publishes-visa-reforms-aimed-at-attracting-skiills</link>
      <description><![CDATA[南非政府宣布对该国工作许可规定进行重大修改，以吸引更多专业人士进入其技术匮乏的经济体并发展旅游业。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-09/south-africa-publishes-visa-reforms-aimed-at-attracting-skiills</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 09 Oct 2024 09:16:32 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>被针对的锡克教分离主义分子称印度仍想置他于死地</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-09/sikh-separatist-targeted-in-us-says-india-still-wants-him-dead</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据称，印度策划了一起暗杀阴谋，但未获成功。这名美国锡克教分离主义者表示，新德里的情报人员仍然想杀死他，并表示拜登政府的“静默外交”未能阻止印度总理纳伦德拉·莫迪的政府。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-09/sikh-separatist-targeted-in-us-says-india-still-wants-him-dead</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 09 Oct 2024 06:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>哥伦比亚法官调查竞选资金时，Petro 宣称发动政变</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-08/colombia-magistrates-to-probe-president-petro-s-campaign-funding</link>
      <description><![CDATA[哥伦比亚选举委员会对古斯塔沃·佩特罗 (Gustavo Petro) 总统竞选活动违反融资限制的指控展开调查后，哥伦比亚资产周三暴跌。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-08/colombia-magistrates-to-probe-president-petro-s-campaign-funding</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 08 Oct 2024 21:24:39 GMT</pubDate>
